\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f1\fs24\lang9 Overview\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f0\fs22\lang9 VerseInserter is a Windows desktop application that automatically inserts Bible verses into Microsoft Word documents. Built with Python architecture, it offers high performance, security, and reliability.\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f1\fs22\lang9 Key Features\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f0\fs22\lang9\u8226?\tab Automatic Verse Insertion: Replaces \cf2\b {{John 3:16}}\cf0\b0  placeholders with actual scripture text\line
\u8226?\tab Multiple Translations: Support for NIV, KJV, ESV, NKJV, and NLT\line
\u8226?\tab High Performance: Processes 100+ verses in seconds using async operations\line
\u8226?\tab Intelligent Caching: Minimizes API calls with multi-tier caching\line
\u8226?\tab Modern UI: Beautiful, responsive interface built with ttkbootstrap\line
\u8226?\tab Secure: Encrypted API key storage with cryptography\line
\u8226?\tab Real-time Progress: Live status updates and comprehensive logging\line
\u8226?\tab Auto-backup: Automatic document backup before processing\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f1\fs24\lang9 Usage Guide\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f1\fs22\lang9 Basic Workflow\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f0\fs22\lang9 1.\tab \b Launch Application\b0\line
2.\tab \b Configure API Key:\b0  Go to Settings and enter your API.Bible key\line
3.\tab \b Select Document:\b0  Click "Browse for Document..." and choose your .docx file\line
4.\tab \b Choose Translation:\b0  Select your preferred Bible translation\line
5.\tab \b Process:\b0  Click "Process Document" and wait for completion\line
6.\tab \b Review:\b0  Check the output file (original_filled.docx) in the same directory\par

